sentences: Peter Mensch (born March 28, 1953) is an American music manager.
In 1982, Mensch formed the management company Q Prime with Cliff Burnstein.
His sister, Barbara Sena Mensch, was the youngest hostage of the Dawson's Field hijackings of September 6, 1970.
Mensch graduated from Scarsdale High School in 1971.
In 2014, he did not return to manage AC/DC, but hinted that the band were to headline the Saturday night at Glastonbury Festival in 2015.

On February 17, 2011 in Manhattan courthouse, he married his third wife, Louise Mensch, former member of British Parliament, despite their political differences (Louise alleges that Peter is a communist).

They managed Led Zeppelin for their reunion show, and Jimmy Page as a solo artist for several years after that.
